My family and I loved this two movie series.  It is worth the money spent for the two movie bundle.  I think that the movies are G rated; however, there may be scenes that a child under the age of 10 might find scary.  So, it is best watched with a parent or an adult that the child can feel comfortable asking questions or that can explain certain scenes to them.  But, for the most part I think that these are nice family time movies that can be shared over and over again.
